title: #92Noon!  9am Hour 8/10 - Mike Florio, Peter Carline
description: Mike Florio joins to discuss the latest in the NFL & Peter Carline of the Daily Mail stops by TCO to talk covering the Vikings from overseas, how people in England perceive the MLS, Tottenham Hotspur Stadium, & more!
